{
  "texts": [
    "This is one of the challenges in computer vision that has received the greatest attention from researchers.",
    "Both Discriminator and Generator networks make use of Convolutional layers.",
    "However, whereas the activation function of the Generator network is the Parametric ReLU, the activation function of the Discriminator network is the Leaky ReLU.",
    "The Generator takes the data that is inputted and calculates the average of all the different pixel wise solutions that are feasible.",
    "SS-GAN (Self Supervised GAN)Unsupervised representation learning is successfully accomplished using self-supervised (SS) learning."
  ]
}